Where we going?

70
00:03:31,986 --> 00:03:33,186
楼上
Upstairs.

71
00:03:35,355 --> 00:03:37,323
发生了什么 Leon 
What's happening, Leon?

72
00:03:37,325 --> 00:03:39,025
在安全模式下
In secure mode,

73
00:03:39,027 --> 00:03:43,39
