MTAC sensors constantly scan for electronic signals.

74
00:03:43,398 --> 00:03:45,615
如果除我们设备外的其它东西
Anything other than our equipment

75
00:03:45,617 --> 00:03:48,284
发射无线电频率 房间就会被封锁
