87
00:04:11,425 --> 00:04:13,860
-错误警报 软件故障 -可能是
- False alarm? Software glitch? - Possible.

88
00:04:13,862 --> 00:04:15,278
这是不是表明 我们可以
Does that mean we're free to let

89
00:04:15,280 --> 00:04:17,280
让我们重要的商业合作伙伴离开了 主任
our valued corporate partners go, Director?

90
00:04:17,282 --> 00:04:19,148
可以解除封锁了 伙计们
You can take us off lockdown, fellas.

91
