Just remember,I have mouths to feed.

99
00:04:48,346 --> 00:04:49,929
两条金鱼
Two goldfish.

100
00:04:49,931 --> 00:04:51,463
我是家里唯一的顶梁柱
I'm their only source of income,

101
00:04:51,465 --> 00:04:53,632
并且它们 它们无比可爱
and they're-they're awfully cute.

102
00:04:53,634 --> 00:04:56,102
放轻松 DiNozzo 我和你一样迫不及待
Relax, DiNozzo. I'm as anxious about this as you are.

103
00:05:05,996 --> 00:05:08,531
我必须要检查下你的口袋 女士 
I'm gonna have to search your pockets, ma'am.

104
00:05:08,533 --> 00:05:10,416
你是否携带任何尖锐的东西
Do you have any needles or sharp objects?

105
00:05:10,418 --> 00:05:11,483
我必须得问
I have to ask.

106
00:05:11,485 --> 00:05:13,753
没有 你继续吧
No. Proceed.

107
00:05:21,428 --> 00:05:22,962
一只笔
A pen?

108
00:05:22,964 --> 00:05:26,132
我还真担心了一阵子呢 先生们 
You had me worried for a moment, gentlemen.

109
00:05:32,439 --> 00:05:33,856
这鬼东西是什么
The the hell's that?

110
00:05:33,858 --> 00:05:36,776
第一印象 这是个闪存盘
Well, first impression,it's a flash drive

111
00:05:36,778 --> 00:05:38,677
