connected to a pinhole microphone.

112
00:05:38,679 --> 00:05:40,396
我们找到窃听器了
We got our bug.

113
00:05:40,398 --> 00:05:42,615
我就是那个漏洞
I'm the breach.

114
00:05:55,608 --> 00:05:57,294
我们先把话说明吧
Okay, let's clear the air right now.

115
