非机密的研究工作
unclassified research in here.

202
00:10:02,873 --> 00:10:05,407
我们讨论过第一条规定的 Flynn
I thought we discussed rule number one, Flynn.

203
00:10:05,409 --> 00:10:07,760
如果我带着耳机 就闪一下台灯
When my earbuds are in, flash the desk light.

204
00:10:07,762 --> 00:10:08,794
