你连看都没看
You didn't even look at it.

210
00:10:20,591 --> 00:10:22,424
这是我进NSA上班的第三天写的
I wrote it my third day at the NSA.

211
00:10:22,426 --> 00:10:23,475
一个星期三的早晨
It was a Wednesday morning.

212
00:10:23,477 --> 00:10:26,028
我刚吃完一盒可可麦片
I just finished a box of Cocoa Pebbles.

213
00:10:27,030 --> 00:10:28,947
