244
00:11:36,600 --> 00:11:39,134
Flynn 你的确是粉丝
Flynn, you <i>are</i> a fan.

245
00:11:39,136 --> 00:11:40,669
什么事 Duck
Yeah, Duck?

246
00:11:41,888 --> 00:11:44,273
