Yep, we're on our way back.

247
00:11:44,275 --> 00:11:46,024
我们发现了另一支窃听笔
We have got a second pen.

248
00:11:46,026 --> 00:11:47,309
我想这意味着
So I guess this means

249
00:11:47,311 --> 00:11:48,727
-我得跟你们一起回去 -不
- I'm riding with you guys.- No.

250
00:11:48,729 --> 00:11:49,862
她跟我们一起走
No, but she is.

251
00:11:49,864 --> 00:11:51,947
什么 为什么
What? Why?

252
00:11:55,535 --> 00:11:58,019
因为 就像你说的
'Cause, like you said,

253
00:11:58,021 --> 00:12:00,989
你写了这个剧本 是吧
you wrote the playbook, right?

254
00:12:13,586 --> 00:12:15,537
我们在这里干什么
What are we doing here?

255
00:12:15,539 --> 00:12:17,756
我在等Ducky 我们的M.E
I'm waiting for Ducky, our M.E.

256
00:12:19,092 --> 00:12:20,709
就是法医
That stands for "medical examiner."

257
00:12:20,711 --> 00:12:24,062
我不是第一次参与案件
This isn't my first case.

258
00:12:24,064 --> 00:12:26,548
我是说 我在这里干什么
I meant, what am <i>I</i> doing here?

259
00:12:26,550 --> 00:12:28,383
我分析全方位的数据
I analyze big-picture data,

260
00:12:28,385 --> 00:12:31,653
在全球反恐战争中提供详细的策略
present detailed strategies in the global war on terror.

261
00:12:32,722 --> 00:12:35,657
或许得花很多年才能真正落实的棋局
Chess moves that can take years to implement.

262
00:12:35,659 --> 00:12:37,492
你喜欢玩棋盘游戏
You enjoy playing board games?

263
00:12:38,946 --> 00:12:41,530
听着 我所能告诉你的一切都在那份报告里
Look, everything I can offer you is in that report.

264
00:12:41,532 --> 00:12:43,064
我本人在这里能起什么作用
What good can I do in person?

265
00:12:43,066 --> 00:12:44,750
我不知道 但是你可以
I don't know,but you can start

266
00:12:44,752 --> 00:12:46,168
开始读这份卷宗 赶上我们的进度
