267
00:12:46,170 --> 00:12:47,536
没错
Yes.

268
00:12:47,538 --> 00:12:50,038
那你能告诉我要多长时间吗
Well, then, can you tell me how long?

269
00:12:50,040 --> 00:12:51,924
我当然能等
Of course I can hold on.

270
00:12:51,926 --> 00:12:54,843
我觉得你不是FBI 也不是来告诉我
I don't suppose you're from the FBI and you've come to tell me

271
00:12:54,845 --> 00:12:56,428
整件事情都是误会
that all this is a misunderstanding?

272
00:12:56,430 --> 00:12:57,512
不好意思 我来自NSA 名叫...
Sorry, NSA. My name...

273
00:12:57,514 --> 00:12:59,765
这毫不相干
That is totally irrelevant.

274
00:12:59,767 --> 00:13:02,134
10分钟之前我还跟他说过话
I was just talking to the man ten minutes ago.

