00:13:02,136 --> 00:13:04,636
特区法医在躲我的电话
The D.C. M.E. is dodging my calls.

276
00:13:04,638 --> 00:13:06,688
Duck 我以为这是关于另一个窃听器
Duck, I thought this was about another bug,

