into an offshore account or he leaks the intel.

362
00:16:17,368 --> 00:16:18,484
我们能追踪这个邮件吗
Can we track the communication?

363
00:16:18,486 --> 00:16:19,785
不行 幕后之人
No, who's ever behind this knows their way

364
00:16:19,787 --> 00:16:21,269
懂计算机代码 也知道如何隐藏行踪
around computer code and knows how to hide.

365
00:16:21,271 --> 00:16:22,237
