much less taxpayer money.

372
00:16:36,286 --> 00:16:38,286
我也是 但是就像我在NSA告诉上司的那样
Neither do I,but like I told my boss at NSA,

373
00:16:38,288 --> 00:16:39,672
这是做生意必须付出的代价
it's the cost of doing business.

374
00:16:39,674 --> 00:16:41,390
如果我们往账户里存了钱
If we deposit the money into the account

375
00:16:41,392 --> 00:16:43,809
而他进入账户 我们就有机会追踪他
and he accesses it, it gives us something to trace.

376
00:16:43,811 --> 00:16:44,843
在我的报告里都概述过了
It's all outlined in my paper.

377
00:16:44,845 --> 00:16:47,179
有可能我们的间谍正用同一份报告
Would that be the same paper our spy

378
00:16:47,181 --> 00:16:48,897
作为他的行动步骤
could be using as a paint-by-numbers?

379
00:16:48,899 --> 00:16:50,099
