He'll know that's our strategy.

380
00:16:50,101 --> 00:16:51,433
就算没有报告 他也早就猜到了
He would have guessed it anyway,

381
00:16:51,435 --> 00:16:53,268
我们可以用NSA的编码去破解他的
which makes it our NSA codes against his.

382
00:16:53,270 --> 00:16:56,689
从统计学上看 这对我们更有利
And statistically,the odds are in our favor.

383
00:16:57,691 --> 00:16:59,608
这是我们找到他的最好办法
It's our best way of finding him.

384
00:16:59,610 --> 00:17:00,909
数据统计不会说谎
Statistics don't lie.

385
00:17:00,911 --> 00:17:02,528
-对 但坏人会 -撒谎
