Unless he hasn't shown his full hand.

390
00:17:11,788 --> 00:17:13,622
继续搜查 直到我们找到他
Keep digging till we find it.

391
00:17:13,624 --> 00:17:16,208
这根本...根本说不通
That doesn't...doesn't make sense.

392
00:17:16,210 --> 00:17:17,710
有些时候你得相信直觉
Sometimes you got to go with your gut.

393
00:17:17,712 --> 00:17:20,045
好吧 但和直觉相比 我想我们都同意
Sure, but gut logic aside, I think we can all agree here

394
00:17:20,047 --> 00:17:22,264
这种情况下 遵循逻辑更好
that actual logic is better.

395
00:17:22,266 --> 00:17:23,632
