And a very nice mustache.

475
00:21:06,890 --> 00:21:08,857
我不知道这是否意在讽刺
I wonder if it's supposed to be ironic.

476
00:21:08,859 --> 00:21:10,409
我们监视他将近一年了
He's been on our radar for about a year.

477
00:21:10,411 --> 00:21:13,245
啊哈 而且他是一个美国公民
Aha, hmm, and he is an American citizen.

478
00:21:13,247 --> 00:21:16,114
这正是为什么我们需要法院指令
Which is exactly why we needed a court order.

479
00:21:16,116 --> 00:21:17,916
我记得我几个月前读过他的档案
I remember reading his file a few months ago

480
00:21:17,918 --> 00:21:22,037
那时我在喝一碗奶油蘑菇汤
over a bowl of cream of mushroom soup.

481
00:21:23,506 --> 00:21:25,674
我用食物来联想记忆
I-I food-associate.

482
00:21:25,676 --> 00:21:27,926
哦
Oh.

483
00:21:27,928 --> 00:21:30,963
我只是...只是很惊讶你会画画
I-I'm just... I'm still stuck on the fact that you can draw.

484
00:21:30,965 --> 00:21:34,433
我是说 虽然画得没有Kate好 但还是非常不错
I mean, this isn't Kate good, but it's good good.

485
00:21:34,435 --> 00:21:35,434
谁是Kate
Who's Kate?

486
00:21:35,436 --> 00:21:38,103
