That-that would take a few hours

487
00:21:38,105 --> 00:21:40,722
和一整盒纸巾来讲述
and a whole box of tissues.

488
00:21:40,724 --> 00:21:43,225
好吧 我们应该先发布通缉令
Okay, well, then we should get this BOLO out first,

489
00:21:43,227 --> 00:21:45,777
而且我想查查NSA那边进展得如何了
and I wanted to check up on the NSA operation.

490
00:21:45,779 --> 00:21:47,729
嗯
Mm-hmm.

491
00:21:47,731 --> 00:21:51,566
嘿 Gibbs 你知道Bishop会画画吗
Hey, Gibbs, did you know that Bishop can draw?

492
00:21:51,568 --> 00:21:52,684
是的 她还在这儿
Yeah, she's still here.

493
00:21:52,686 --> 00:21:55,237
为什么
Why?

494
00:21:58,541 --> 00:22:00,375
好的
Okay.

495
00:22:00,377 --> 00:22:02,627
Abby
Abby?

496
00:22:02,629 --> 00:22:04,612
怎么了 是不是有关汇款的事
What? Is it about the money-drop?

497
00:22:04,614 --> 00:22:07,749
也许我们应该谈一谈Kate
Maybe we should have that talk about Kate.

498
00:22:11,287 --> 00:22:13,638
经理听到了枪声 报了警
Manager heard the shots, called the police.

499
00:22:13,640 --> 00:22:15,257
没人看到开枪的人
Nobody saw the shooter.

500
00:22:15,259 --> 00:22:17,592
NSA汇了那笔勒索费
NSA deposited the extortion money,

501
00:22:17,594 --> 00:22:20,628
然后我们的间谍通过咖啡店的无线网络接收
and our spy accessed it using the coffee shop's Wi-Fi.

502
00:22:20,630 --> 00:22:22,597
这可不是我会接收一千万美元的最佳地点
It's not the first place I'd come to collect $10 million.

503
00:22:22,599 --> 00:22:24,466
Flynderling探员也这么想
Agent Flynderling thought the same thing.

504
00:22:24,468 --> 00:22:27,302
所以他没来得及呼叫支援 就先进行跟踪
That's why he came to follow up before calling in a task force.

505
00:22:27,304 --> 00:22:29,688
三次近距离枪杀 正中胸部
Three gunshot wounds to the chest at close range.

506
00:22:29,690 --> 00:22:32,807
根据弹孔的火药残留和身体组织的损伤程度
Based on the stippling and tissue damage,

507
00:22:32,809 --> 00:22:34,192
他没有还手的机会
he never had a chance.

508
00:22:34,194 --> 00:22:35,660
刚刚才从他的汽车里出来
Barely got out of his car.

509
00:22:35,662 --> 00:22:37,112
-伏击 -老大
- Ambushed. - Boss,

510
00:22:37,114 --> 00:22:39,247
他的口袋里有东西
he's got something in his pocket.

511
