嘿 老大 这不是她的...
Hey, boss, isn't this her...

512
00:22:54,847 --> 00:22:57,215
我的报告
My report.

513
00:23:01,687 --> 00:23:03,838
你是对的 Gibbs探员
You were right, Agent Gibbs.

514
00:23:03,840 --> 00:23:06,608
这和那个无关 Bishop
It's not about that, Bishop.

515
00:23:22,171 --> 00:23:26,157
有人在海军部长的身上放置了监听器
Somebody plants a surveillance device on the Secretary of the Navy,

517
00:23:26,159 --> 00:23:27,759
敲诈了美国政府
and extorts the U.S. Government.

518
00:23:27,761 --> 00:23:33,014
很可能和在特区验尸房里偷第二支监听笔的冒牌FBI探员是同一个人
Likely the same guy who posed as an FBI agent to steal a second spy pen from the D.C. morgue.

520
00:23:33,015 --> 00:23:34,315
Rudolph Stalin--
Rudolph Stalin--

521
00:23:34,317 --> 00:23:36,851
他因把美国情报出售给俄罗斯人而被通缉
he's an American wanted for selling U.S. intel to Russia.

523
00:23:36,853 --> 00:23:38,319
有着那样的名字和那样的小胡子
