00:23:39,772 --> 00:23:41,155
但是当NSA试图
But when the NSA tried

526
00:23:41,157 --> 00:23:42,606
汇款给他并追踪那笔存款时
to pay him off and track the deposit...

527
00:23:42,608 --> 00:23:44,325
